data.description: This beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is located in the desirable Steeple Chase neighborhood. Desirable school district and a close commute to Fort Bragg. Spacious living area and formal dining! Four great sized rooms, one guest bedroom has an attached office. Large fully fenced in back yard. 2 car garage with Tesla charger already installed!! $2,000 buyer concessions with acceptable offer. Get your private showing scheduled today!
